<l>kāṇiṟ kuvaḷai kaviḻntu nilanōkkum </l>
<l>māṇiḻai kaṇṇovvē meṉṟu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>If the blue lotus could see, it would stoop and look at the ground saying, "I can never resemble the eyes of this excellent jewelled one."</l>
